Description: Provides access to the 'Stat-Xplore Open Data API'. The API 
    contains data on the UK benefits system, as available on the 'Stat-Xplore'
    web service (<https://stat-xplore.dwp.gov.uk/>). See 
    <https://stat-xplore.dwp.gov.uk/webapi/online-help/Open-Data-API.html> 
    for full API documentation.
